  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t有不少游客/美食家，对全国各省驻京办餐厅的美食赞不绝口，不出北京即可以尝到大江南北长城内外的全国美味佳肴，还写了各驻京办美食指引，同好们争相附和，大家踊跃分享，欢乐开怀；<br/>\n<br/>\r\n另一面，这些驻京办都担负着截访本省访民、维稳遮羞、利益输送、贿赂腐败的功能，还勾结黑社会黑监狱，访民们号哭绝望，生不如死。然而游客/美食家们并不了解访民遭遇，甚至了解但并不关心在乎，觉得和自己无关，坦然享受美食。撕裂的中国，天堂地狱就在一处<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYzFlN2IzOTZhMWVkZmZlZjJiNmQzLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c1e7b396a1edffef2b6d3.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c1e7b396a1edffef2b6d3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c1e7b396a1edffef2b6d3.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMmNkZDcyN2VhZDc2OWUzZTViZDRlLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2cdd727ead769e3e5bd4e.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2cdd727ead769e3e5bd4e.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/2cdd727ead769e3e5bd4e.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTgzZWQ1YmZkM2Y1OTJiNzJiNmRlLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e83ed5bfd3f592b72b6de.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e83ed5bfd3f592b72b6de.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e83ed5bfd3f592b72b6de.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTllZWYzMzEyZDZlMjY1ZWNjNWQ4LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/59eef3312d6e265ecc5d8.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/59eef3312d6e265ecc5d8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/59eef3312d6e265ecc5d8.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDVlYjg4MzZjOGNlNjc0ZWM3OGFkLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow no